# Alternate-Family Specialist Review: Issue #623 Implementation Slice

**Reviewer:** Claude Opus 4.6 (alternate-family specialist)
**Review scope:** Bounded implementation slice for issue #623 — mutation-time pre-tool fail-closed hardening
**Date:** 2026-04-30
**Status:** `accepted`

